{
  "stem": "14900.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I was told that if I cried and begged the head couple might take pity on me, since neither one of us had been selected for the gas chamber, and maybe bring my mother to me or take me back to lager A.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I threw myself in the mud.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "It was pouring.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I cried, and I cried, and I screamed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Pretty soon I couldn't stop it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "I lost all self-control.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Evidently, I must have passed out at a certain point because when I came to I was laying on a dirt ground covered in a tent type of an area.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And there were Polish voices around me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Six Polish Jewesses had heard my screams and they waited till the cover of darkness, went and dragged me inside and proceeded to protect me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "They bathed me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "I had dysentery and I was so debilitated I couldn't stand up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "I'd just keel over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Would you believe in that hell hole, six young women, each one gave up one piece of her potato for me?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We formed a group.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Two of them had belonged to the Communist party, three of them, actually, in the Lodz Ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I really didn't know what communism was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But to me it was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was true form of communism.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One for all, all for one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Share, share alike.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And with that one extra bite of their potato, which multiplied, was six bites of either potato or cabbage or whatever, I regained sufficient strength.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They held me up during the countdowns and all, that they support me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They surrounded me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As I started falling they'd push me, every which way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I got strong enough and there was a transport.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't know where to.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
